        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Rubbish, absolute rubbish.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3ea42e6a-f60d-4428-82b6-93b936002bd9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
