<p class="">If that situation did arise, would the hon. Member mind saying what action he would recommend that this country should take?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-699a648a-1a5e-4341-9a8f-70873a5027e7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
