<p class="">Would the right hon. Gentleman recognise both sides as belligerents?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-47892e2b-e85e-4026-a2e3-add1029a16f4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
